Bring a large pot of salted water to a boil. Combine tomatoes, avocados, mozzarella, basil, olive oil and lemon juice in a large bowl. Season with salt and pepper. Let mixture marinate for 20 to 30 minutes. Cook PLUS(R) Elbows 1 minute less than recommended package cooking time. Drain and pour onto a flat surface. Drizzle with a small amount of oil and let cool. Add cooled pasta to ingredients in bowl; toss and serve.